high_descs: Turn left, go towards the wall, turn left, go across the room, turn left and then turn left toward the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn right, go toward the fridge, turn right and then turn right to the counter.
Cut the bread on the counter.
Turn left, go to the wall, turn left towards the trash can.
Put the knife in the trash can.
Turn left and go back to the counter.
Pick a slice of bread.
Turn around and head to the fridge.
Put the slice of bread in the fridge, close the fridge, open the fridge and pick it back up.
Turn right, go to the wall and turn left to the trash can.
Put the slice of bread in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled slice of bread in the trash can.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the far end of the island countertop.
Pick up the knife with yellow handle on the counter.
Turn right and left and stop at the first loaf of bread on the counter.
Slice the first loaf of bread just the right half of it that is sitting on the counter top.
Turn left and face the garbage can on the left.
Place the knife in the black garbage bin in the corner on your left
Turn left and walk to the loaf of bread on the counter you sliced.
Pick up the farthest left slice of bread.
Turn left and walk to the refrigerator
Open the refrigerator door and place the bread on top shelf and close the door then open and take it out
Turn right and walk to the garbage can in the corner.
Place the slice of bread in the garbage can.
anns.task_desc: Place a slice of chilled bread in the garbage can.

high_descs: Turn around and walk around to face the far end of the center table.
Pick up the knife on the center table.
Walk to the right around the corner of the counter and turn left to face the bread on the left.
Cut the bread on the left into slices.
Turn around and step forward to face the fridge.
Place the knife in the fridge.
Turn around to face the bread on the counter.
Pick up a slice of bread on the counter.
Turn around to face the fridge.
Place the bread slice in the fridge and remove it.
Turn around and step forward to face the trash can.
Place the bread slice in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: To cool a bread slice and place it in the trash can.
